Method 2: Using a Calculator

Step 1: Divide 987,670 by 128 using a calculator. The result is approximately 7716.640625.

Step 2: The integer part of the quotient is 7716. Multiply 7716 by 128:
7716 × 128 = 987,648

Step 3: Subtract the result from the dividend:
987,670 - 987,648 = 22
The whole number remainder when 987,670 is divided by 128 is $\boxed{22}$.

